result.name: Ming's Kitchen

reviews.text: Overall food is tasty. Fried rice, noodle and BBQ port are excellent

Great Hong Kong style cafe. Has a large menu with a lot of choices. They even serve BBQ items (soya chicken, roast pork, bbq pork, etc.) And some dim sum. Their breakfast, lunch, and tea-time (till 6 pm) is well priced with decent portions. We actually found their dim sum relatively tasty for a place that doesn't specialize in this type of cuisine. We love the variety of choices. Place seems decently clean and service is prompt. It's pretty standard to what you can expect in Hong Kong. They have English menus with some photos so it's not too hard to figure things out. Close to bus depot that has buses threat takes you to China and Macau so it's pretty busy. Worth checking out if you like Chinese food but not sure what you feel like.

Good restaurant. Food was tasty (and very oily). Lots of variety. 

Pros: not too expensive, good food. 

Cons: I saw two male cooks exit the restroom without washing their hands. Can’t say the tables were too clean, either.
A good favour local HK tea- restaurant chain.

result.name: Ming Zhan Shao Wei Restaurant

reviews.text:
Food itself was good , I been here for twice for difference type of breakfast , one is dim sum another time was satay beef instant noodle plus luncheon meat with fired egg , buttered bread which was quite nice . But as previous comments from another one , their service were poor and rude , although environments are clean and bright but it minus their score due to bad service provided ! 
I specially like their beverages , from ice coffee to hot milk tea , there are all goods .
I would visiting here another day , hope their service would be improved !

是ㄧ間不錯吃的茶餐廳， 從早餐，點心到燒臘皆有，價錢就是ㄧ般行價 ，飲料部分十分好喝，然則服務有待加強，除了不親切外還很粗暴無禮 !

Terrible service! Their waitress are very rude and unfriendly! Food is oily and tasted very salty. Lots of hidden charges, we were told that the drinks are included in the set dinner but ended up they charged us and extra charge for cold drinks. We DO NOT recommend this restaurant!

reviews.text: 我喜歡這餐室,西式早餐價錢平,食物品質好,又新鮮,又夠熱,環境舒適,老闆招呼好,講英語,國語,没問题。
小拼盤還好……但想品嚐正宗上海風味就欠奉了！！
Overall food is tasty. Fried rice, noodle and BBQ port are excellent
食品好吃還可以！但價錢不大眾化
價錢唔算貴啲嘢食ok
